509
00:22:02,083 --> 00:22:05,500
- OH, WOW.
I'VE GOTTEN STRONGER.

510
00:22:05,583 --> 00:22:07,666
WATCH OUT!
'CAUSE YOU'RE DEALING WITH

511
00:22:07,750 --> 00:22:10,416
